Coins are in random state, some are heads up some are tails up. Experimenter tell Alice number that is in range of squeres on chess board. Considering there are 64 squeres number is from 1 to 64. Alice should turn or not one of the coins on the chess board in such way that Bob could came to this room later and find out this number only by looking on the chess board. What would be the wining strategy?
